  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl combine the sliced cabbage, julienned carrot, and bell pepper.",
    "Add the chopped cilantro and sliced green onions to the bowl.",
    "Sprinkle the papelon, chili flakes, salt, and pepper over the vegetables.",
    "Pour lime juice and olive oil over the mixture and toss until evenly coated.",
    "Gently fold in the bonito flakes, allowing them to shatter and release aroma.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning with more salt, pepper, or lime if desired.",
    "Let the salad rest for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve chilled or at room temperature as a light, spicy Polish-inspired lunch."
